SCRUMIE
------------------------------
Its very simple implementation of scrum board, it can help you with task managment in sprint
when you don't have access to physical board or you work online.

Instalation:

    requirements: 
     * PHP 5.3+
     * http server (eg Apache)

    database:
     * scrumie use sqlite database that should be placed inside data folder as scrumie.sqlite file
       you can use template database:

           cp data/scrumie.sqlite.dist data/scrumie.sqlite

       and login to scrumie as domo:demo 
